{"tid":2156013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅磚牆執仔「為學生樣樣可以放低」","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:41:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"712d9c3b8bfbaef088d479d7caeef4f2e784f7f7","tid":2156013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/MGWKHCIARRHP7D7GLPQ5M2KQ6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FMGWKHCIARRHP7D7GLPQ5M2KQ6Y%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=1396e4d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FMGWKHCIARRHP7D7GLPQ5M2KQ6Y%2F&h=9f4068a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/MGWKHCIARRHP7D7GLPQ5M2KQ6Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n紅磚牆執仔「為學生樣樣可以放低」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/68qtXiQa5oB8-rdCWkAj7-yng3M=/1575x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X3UK7V3NSNEIXNFB3DVJSTFVFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F68qtXiQa5oB8-rdCWkAj7-yng3M%3D%2F1575x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX3UK7V3NSNEIXNFB3DVJSTFVFA.jpg&h=2aa217b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■理大圍城一役，鄧振強（左）與多間學校校長入內執仔。<br />\n<br />\n鄧振強退休前一年擔任中學校長會主席，原打算只做接班過渡者，豈料經歷香港歷史性轉變。他指上任初期經常難以入睡，甚至因承受巨大壓力而變瘦；但面對過去一年的社會事件，他對學界仍然願意以學生利益為先感欣慰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牽涉年輕人 選擇站出來<br />\n<br />\n投身教育界38年，34歲便成為香港管理專業協會羅桂祥中學的創校校長，霎眼已26年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他坦言擔任主席相當吃力，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n鄧振強。。。。。。。。。。。。：究竟須與社會事件保持距離？還是主動關注？結果因牽涉年輕人，他遵從該會傳統選擇了後者，在很多重大事件上站出來表達意見。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「教育核心係育人，人係最緊要。學校存在就因為有學生，所以每一個學生都係重要。」過去一年令他感受至深的是，不同學校對學生的堅持。<br />\n<br />\n「無論社會點樣變動，點樣有矛盾及衝突，甚至是校長老師與學生有不同政治見解，但大家都堅持學生係最重要。」他以理大事件為例，當時各校長收到學生求助時，都沒考慮太多，一心想幫學生，「原來大家喺學生利益為先的情況下，樣樣嘢都可以放低。」"},{"pid":"acf6272994ddc83a9425e22f434d7ed33eddcb51","tid":2156013,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f54876e7367acfff1ea234dafcdb5fcc5648ea","tid":2156013,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9821261f2effb14ecbbd2722fb4fe3cb881271","tid":2156013,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f8023ebf07e6ba8709768a46748cf07503992d87","tid":2156013,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2cc2646197f516781c232e9ad839c3c817fafc2c","tid":2156013,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d57f195c8a6d70f9d97acb31dd01b40d9704142","tid":2156013,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"01a3d56905422a0021eb05ec1cffd03ef56f8945","tid":2156013,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45a8841e410e62738f03be89ed82d6587a001f5e","tid":2156013,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e72eedab557785834b88bc65c19ea27b78691d43","tid":2156013,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98fBCfR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http